abstract_ssm: Two photographs date from circa 1930 and pertain to the construction of the New York City subway. Included is an exterior view of elevated subway line construction at 4th Avenue and 9th Street in Brooklyn and an interior view of underground subway construction showing two excavation workers in a subway tunnel.
